description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Challe is on a journey to find diamonds in caves. Many dangerous traps or enemies can hurt Challe on her way through the caves.  Beware of poisonous slime, acid, explosions and hostile creatures.
